奥利维亚·穆恩 (Olivia Munn) 表示医生通过“积极”的癌症治疗挽救了她的生命https://www.nme.com/news/film/olivia-munn-says-doctor-saved-her-life-with-aggressive-cancer-treatment-3758495?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=olivia-munn-says-医生通过积极的癌症治疗挽救了她的生命Max PilleyWed, 22 May 2024 11:54:07 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3758495 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/olivia_munn_photo.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="奥利维亚·穆恩" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/olivia_munn_photo.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/olivia_munn_photo-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/olivia_munn_photo-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/olivia_munn_photo-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/olivia_munn_photo-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/olivia_munn_photo-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “她是我的守护天使”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/olivia-munn-says-doctor-saved-her-life-with-aggressive-cancer-treatment-3758495">奥利维亚·穆恩 (Olivia Munn) 表示医生通过“积极”的癌症治疗挽救了她的生命，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/olivia_munn_photo.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="奥利维亚·穆恩" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/olivia_munn_photo.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/olivia_munn_photo-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/olivia_munn_photo-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/olivia_munn_photo-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/olivia_munn_photo-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/olivia_munn_photo-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>奥利维亚·穆恩 (Olivia Munn) 表示，建议积极治疗她的乳腺癌的医生“确实拯救了我的生命”。</p><p>这位演员于 3 月份分享了自己确诊的消息，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/olivia-munn-reveals-breast-cancer-diagnosis-3600935">并在社交媒体上确认，她在“为了积极主动地关注自己的健康”而进行了基因测试后，于 2023 年 4 月首次收到了这一信息</a>。</p><p>虽然她通过了初步测试，但两个月后她发现自己患有乳腺癌。</p><p>这位因在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/new-x-men-apocalypse-footage-unleashes-the-four-ho-876653"><i>《X战警：天启》</i></a>中饰演灵蝶以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/the-predator-new-trailer-2018-2345401"><i>《铁血战士》</i></a> 、 <i>《约会之夜》</i>和<i>《魔力麦克》</i>等电影而闻名的演员写道：“在过去的十个月里，我做了四次手术，很多天都在床上度过。我什至无法数数，但我对癌症、癌症治疗和激素的了解比我想象的还要多。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C4dXfrULDdJ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><p